{{Top|leg}}
A '''pinnace''' was a fast, short-range [[Starship/Legends|starship]] that was carried aboard a larger vessel. Pinnaces were typically slightly larger than [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] and had some cargo space; as a result, they were deployed in combat and supply roles. The [[2 Warpod|Ulig Abaha Ltd. #2 Warpod]] was a pinnace.

==Behind the scenes==
In the real world, a [[Wikipedia:Pinnace (ship's boat)|''pinnace'']] was a small boat, propelled by either sails or oars, that was commonly used for scouting and small raids.

